post_call_analysis_data.name: first_name
post_call_analysis_data.description: Customer's first name, verified and spelled if unclear

post_call_analysis_data.name: car_make_model
post_call_analysis_data.description: Vehicle make and model (e.g. Toyota Camry, Ford F-150)

post_call_analysis_data.name: service_type
post_call_analysis_data.description: Type of auto service: Oil Change, Brake Service, Tires, Body Work, or Repairs

post_call_analysis_data.name: text_optin
post_call_analysis_data.description: Whether customer opted in to receive text message updates

post_call_analysis_data.name: insurance_name
post_call_analysis_data.description: Insurance company name (for Body Work or Repairs only). Empty if not applicable.

post_call_analysis_data.name: insurance_policy_number
post_call_analysis_data.description: Insurance policy number (for Body Work or Repairs only). Empty if not applicable.

post_call_analysis_data.name: claim_agent_name
post_call_analysis_data.description: Insurance claims agent name. N/A if customer doesn't know. Empty if not applicable.

post_call_analysis_data.name: claim_agent_email
post_call_analysis_data.description: Insurance claims agent email address. N/A if not available. Empty if not applicable.

post_call_analysis_data.name: claim_agent_number
post_call_analysis_data.description: Insurance claims agent phone number. N/A if not available. Empty if not applicable.

post_call_analysis_data.name: upsell_interested
post_call_analysis_data.description: Whether customer expressed interest in the radiator flush/coolant replacement upsell (Tires + high mileage only). True if interested in pricing or email quote, false if declined.
